This is the tool used by Sunday Night Film Club (SNFC) hosts to send out the
weekly newsletter to multiple services (email, livejournal, wordpress,
twitter, etc). 

(c)2010-2025 Sean Graham (sean-graham.com)

Local testing
-------------

- Copy `config.example.json` to `config.json` and adjust values for your environment.
- Run the web app: `python app.py` then open the form.
- Or run the CLI test tool to invoke plugins directly:

```
python testtool.py --help
python testtool.py --plugin "SNFC Mailing List" --film "Example" --time 7:30pm
```

You can specify a config path via `--config` or `SNFC_CONFIG` env variable.
